#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Dead_Water/scenarios/02_Flight.cfg:117
#: data/campaigns/Dead_Water/scenarios/02_Flight.cfg:141
#: data/campaigns/Dead_Water/scenarios/02_Flight.cfg:160
